sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Job as Scheduled Job
  participant SLA as SLA Service
  participant Notify as Notification Service
  participant Audit as Audit Service
  participant Ops as Operations Console
  Job->>SLA: Scan active timers
  SLA->>SLA: Detect warning/breach
  SLA->>Notify: Queue notification
  SLA->>Audit: Record SLA warning/breach/escalation
  SLA->>Ops: Update health/ageing projection
  Ops-->>SLA: Admin views escalation state
